paragraphs.text:
%sql
SELECT m.movieId, m.title, COUNT(r.rating) as ratings_count, MEAN(r.rating) as ratings_mean
FROM ratings as r
INNER JOIN movies as m on m.movieID = r.movieID
GROUP BY m.movieID, m.title
ORDER BY ratings_count DESC
LIMIT 1000
